.TH DAP2P 1 "2026-01-02" "dumbass-tree" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
dap2p \- peer-to-peer link helpers (ethernet + USB gadget)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B dap2p
[--dry-run] [-v] <command>
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B eth up <iface> <addr>
Bring iface up + add static IPv4 address (two-tier warning).
.TP
.B gadget net
Load g_ether (USB Ethernet gadget) on gadget-capable hardware.
.TP
.B gadget msd <backing_file>
Expose file as USB mass storage (g_mass_storage).
.TP
.B gadget off
Unload gadget modules (best-effort).
